OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening with some late sunny spells.
OL,7,FOccasional showers develop through the
OL,8,Fearly hours, becoming heavier and more
OL,9,Ffrequent, especially across the
OL,10,FLothians, with a risk of thunder,
OL,11,Flater.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA rather cloudy day with
OL,14,Foccasional rain, heavy and thundery
OL,15,Frain at times. Some drier spells of
OL,16,Fweather too. Warm and humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
