OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FBright
OL,6,Fin east Saturday, otherwise rather
OL,7,Fcloudy with occasional rain, becoming
OL,8,Fpersistent later in west. Sunday and
OL,9,FMonday see sunny spells and showers
OL,10,Fwith occasionally fresh southwesterly
OL,11,Fwind. Much cooler.
